tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE health_outcomes (
  study_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  participant_id INT,
  step_count INT,
  heart_rate INT,
  blood_pressure VARCHAR(20),
  duration_of_study INT
);

CREATE TABLE HealthOutcomeData (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    outcome_type VARCHAR(50),
    outcome_value INT,
    date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE StudyParticipants (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    location VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE HealthOutcomes (
   id INT PRIMARY KEY,
   user_id INT,
   heart_rate INT,
   blood_pressure INT,
   bmi FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE StudyData (
   id INT PRIMARY KEY,
   user_id INT,
   study_date DATE,
   study_time TIME,
   study_location TEXT
);
